data.description: The home with the white picket fence you've always wanted has arrived! Move in ready with a great layout and parking large enough for your RV and vehicles! The back yard is fenced also for the chickens or your furry friends. The coop can stay or go, your choice! The 24x30 garage has a concrete floor, insulation, electric and a side door for easy convenience. There is also a set up for a potential wood stove or propane furnace to meet all of your seasonal needs. The main floor has a large, beautiful kitchen with a breakfast island, pantry and room for a kitchen table, living area, 2 bedrooms, bathroom, attic fan, linen closet and a sliding glass door that leads out to the large deck. The finished, walk-out basement has the gas fireplace, a spot for an additional bedroom, a large double closet, more storage areas and still room for game night! With all of this to offer and an amazing location, this home is sure to go fast! Make your appointment today!
